A man will only put in work for a woman he really wants. So don’t waste your time holding on to someone who isn’t consistent with positive actions, and willing to pour into the relationship what is needed for success and happiness.

Be sure to watch the full video here 👉 https://youtu.be/38HI-lQBlH0 👈 titled “If You Want To Know How He Feels About You”
